query.result:
**English:**
52 But just as a coal which gives out flame, 53 and because of its vivid whiteness overcomes it, 54 so that its appearance is preserved;
55 so this lightning which now surrounds us 56 will be overcome in appearance by the flesh 57 which every day the earth covers;
